            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>ANKER 旗下的视听产品 soundcore 系列一直以高性价比见称。最近 Space One Pro 主动降噪头戴式蓝牙耳机到了 unwire 编辑部，虽然 Space One Pro 是一款头戴式耳机，但配合 FlexiCurve 蛇骨式折叠结构，耳机在收纳状态下比佩戴状态细 50%，方便用家日常携带外出听歌唱。以下小编将从设计、佩戴感、降噪、续航、音质等方面分享实际使用体验。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1277075" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc00014-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc00014-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc00014.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2></h2><h2>磨砂材质搭配金属细节，低调典雅不失精致</h2><p>头戴式耳机来说，用家最关心首先当然是音质，另外耳机的外观、便携性和佩戴舒适度亦是购买时需要考虑的重点。下面小编会先从外观说起。耀墨黑和奶油白两色供用家选择，小编收到的是奶油白版本，Space One Pro 在外观设计上走低调精致路线，其外壳采用磨砂材质，搭配金属环装饰，整体设计极具质感，耳机看起来典雅不失细节。即使不听歌时将耳机悬挂于颈间也可作配饰，成为日常穿搭的一部分，迎合现在盛行的 Y2K 流行元素。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1277214" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc00029-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc00029-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc00029.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1277213" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc00047-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc00047-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc00047.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1277210" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc00058-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc00058-